property.value: <expression> evaluate an expression and print its result
? display this help or a help page for a specific command
#callAction call an IDE action with custom parameters
#removeGenSources delete the source_gen, source_gen.caches and classes_gen directories
#show show sequence of nodes/references/models/modules in the Usages View panel
#consoleModel return a model, in which the console commands as well as its history are stored
#internalMode access the IDE internal mode variable
refactor apply a function to manually selected nodes
ofAspect filter models by their aspect
#instances instances of a concept in scope
#usages direct references to a node in scope

task.summary: Initial version of tissue set up language. Added name checking rules to cells, tissues, and corresponding types.
Added new behaviours for cell counting to arrangements. Tissue container can now count all cells, whether they are in a tissue or not.
Complete tissue language. World setup is work-in-progress.
Triangular substrates can now be defined in the world setup language.
Added new checking algorithms to determine whether tissue and cell objects are colliding with each other. Some errors in importing language and collision detection.
Tested checking algorithms. Monolayers should now track other objects and world boundaries.
With a specified run configuration, the DSL can now write files to new locations.
Changed "square" cell shape to rectangular to reflect the ability to change both height and width.
